title: The Real Housewives Of New York City S06E08 Unforgivable Debt WE
description: After standing Sonja up for a sunbathing date, Ramona decides to spill Sonja's financial secrets all over the Hamptons. Meanwhile, back in New York, Kristen meets with a new modeling agent, and is shocked to learn that her modeling days may be over. When Sonja is stood up by her 23-year-old boy toy, she suspects that Ramona had something to do with it.
